manticore.presentation.terminal
Class AdvancedCommandGroup

java.lang.Object
  manticore.presentation.terminal.CommandGroup
      manticore.presentation.terminal.AdvancedCommandGroup

public abstract class AdvancedCommandGroup
extends CommandGroup

Represents a group of terminal commands under a common subject. Provides some handy methods to read/print data from/to the user.
